{"tid":860452,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"搭地鐵有咩技巧？","createTime":"2018-10-13T10:57:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-13T10:59:51.000Z","uid":212998,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d469bcdf29bf81d6a761b9d780af8f0f58f054c3","tid":860452,"uid":212998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T10:57:22.000Z","msg":"好似搭地鐵同人逼都要好有技巧<br />\n今朝搭地鐵搭到去北角站<br />\n我企係門口個扶手位<br />\n見住架車準備開走個一下<br />\n有個肥仔以一個標準嘅跳高姿勢<br />\n魚躍龍門撞左入黎<br />\n成個姿勢好完美<br />\n差在佢跳唔起<br />\n係佢訓練得耐<br />\n定我見識少？<br />\n<br />\n想各位連登仔比啲經歷黎比我開下眼界<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a58f3fd39b5faebfb559cbe646dd6510af7712c","tid":860452,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T10:59:51.000Z","msg":"企近啲去啲雞到<br />\n記住<br />\n全部女人都係雞<br />\n不過地鐵嗰啲係免費"}]}